videos.description: Tyree Jackson hits Anthony Johnson for a 54-yard touchdown pass play to extend the lead for Buffalo.
videos.headline: Jackson connects Johnson for Buffalo TD

videos.description: Nathan Rourke runs in for a 7-yard touchdown to put Ohio on the board in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Rourke rams in for Ohio TD

videos.description: Nathan Rourke connects with Andrew Meyer for a 40-yard gain to put the Bobcats in the red zone.
videos.headline: Rourke to Meyer for big gain for Ohio

videos.description: Nathan Rourke's second touchdown run of the game makes it a one score game in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Rourke scores again for Ohio

videos.description: Nathan Rourke hits Cameron Odom for a 57-yard touchdown to tie the game 24-24 in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Odom TD ties the game for Ohio

videos.description: K.J. Osborn's 39 yard punt return sets up Buffalo 1st-and-goal in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Osborn's electrifying punt return sets up Buffalo
